location.name: MyCity Civic Center
location.description: MyCity Civic Center is located on Main Street and contains facilities for a number of civic and community services available.

service.name: Community Counselling
service.description: Counselling Services provided by trained professionals. Suitable for people with mental health conditions such as anxiety, depression, or eating disorders as well as people experiencing difficult life events and circumstances.
service.fees_description: Non-NHS patients are expected to pay for their counselling sessions. We charge a flat rate per hour of counselling. The current rate is £50 per hour. Please see our website for up to date prices.
